description:
Shaky Kane - Elephantmen and Monsters (2014) (Digital) (DR & Quinch-Empire)


A first for Elephantmen, get this Comixology-exclusive digital-only edition of Elephantmen and Monsters, a special collection of issues co-created by legendary psychedelic artist Shaky Kane.

Contains issues #33, #46, and #56 of Elephantmen, as well as digital-exclusive extras including an insight into Shaky's creative process.
